	<article id="post-4859" class="post-4859 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-photography-interviews tag-backup tag-bob-levitus tag-interview">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/07/03/tfttf642-blown-away-tornado-interview-dr-mac/" rel="bookmark">tfttf642 &#8211; Blown Away By A Tornado &#8211; Interview with Dr. Mac</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/07/03/tfttf642-blown-away-tornado-interview-dr-mac/" title="11:35 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-07-03T23:35:34+00:00">July 3, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/author/ravsitar/" title="View all posts by Ravsitar" rel="author">Ravsitar</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
