				<div class="entry-content">
			<p class="wp-flattr-button"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/?flattrss_redirect&amp;id=4859&amp;md5=e0082b4d1e5d4e0da4ca6346a78a87cb" title="Flattr" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/plugins/flattr/img/flattr-badge-large.png" alt="flattr this!"/></a></p><audio id="podlovewebplayer_5" style="width: auto; height: 30px" controls type="audio/mpeg" preload="none" src="http://www.podtrac.com/pts/redirect.mp3/media.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/tfttf642_blown_away_by_a_tornado.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" preload="none">
